<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249408>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Prionchulus muscorum (Dujardin, 1845) Wu & Hoeppli, 1929 female. A – D: Anterior end. E – H: Subventral wall with denticulate ridge. I: Body region showing excretory pore. J – L: Pharyngo-intestinal junction. M: Vulval region. N, O: Posterior body region. P: tail tip. (Scale bar = 10 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249408/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

